snippet.title: Dave the Diver - Balatro, Potion Craft & Mxmtoon Collaboration Announcement Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Watch a new trailer for Dave the Diver's upcoming collaborations with Balatro, Potion Craft, an Mxmtoon, coming in October on Nintendo Switch PlayStation 4, and PlayStation 5.
